Hello Ella,
&nbsp;
Upon checking from our end, we could see that all the 4 label failed orders have the product "Possessed Magazine - One Size (SKU - 34023-00003)" and for this product, the customs value for US is given as 1.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
Due to the conversion with USD and Euros, 1 USD is considered as 0.86 Euros and the same is passed to FedEx.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
As FedEx need a minimum value of 1 as the customs value, the label generation failed with the error message "Invalid Customs Value".&nbsp;
&nbsp;
So, for the current orders, to resolve the case, please Navigate to the Products -&gt; All Products -&gt; search for the product Possessed Magazine - One Size (SKU - 34023-00003) -&gt; Click on the Variant Name -&gt; Under Country‑Based Custom Values, update the value as 2 and Save.&nbsp;
Once done, let us know. We will reprocess the orders and try generating the label for an order from ur end to check.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
Meanwhile, i will have this case checked with our technical team as well.&nbsp;
&nbsp;

&nbsp;

&nbsp;
Thanks and Regards,
Sagar K S
Team PluginHive

L3 - Label generation is failing with the error message "Invalid Customs Value"
&nbsp;
For the orders 112295, 112261, 112220 and 112259 which are to US, the label generation is failing. All these orders have same product "Possessed Magazine - One Size (SKU - 34023-00003)" and the customer has provided country based customs value selecting US and the value as 1.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
Under the App Settings -&gt; General Settings -&gt; Shipping, the Preferred Shipment Currency is provided as Shipment Source Currency and the Minimum Value for Customs/Insured Amount is 1.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
In the label request, the customs amount passed is 0.86 Euros (converted from 1 USD to 0.86 Euros) and as this has not met carrier's minimum criteria, the label generation failed.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
Also, we are not sure why the minimum value 1 is not considered in this case.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
I have attached the Request Response XMLs of a label failed order for reference.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
This has been checked with Keerthi as well.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
So, could you please check about this case and provide an update?
&nbsp;
Store URL - satisfyrunning.myshopify.com&nbsp;
App - Shopify MCSL

